                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-3">
                <p class="text-sm text-yellow-700">
                  <strong>Still have questions?</strong> If you can't find the answer to your question here, please check our support page or contact our support team directly.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Need More Help?</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
                Our support team is here to help with any questions not covered in this FAQ.
              </p>
              <a href="/support" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
                Contact Support
              </a>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Join the Community</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
                Connect with other Baldrick users in our Facebook group for tips and advice.
              </p>
              <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/baldrickboards" target="_blank" class="inline-block bg-purple-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-purple-700 transition-colors">
                Join Facebook Group
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Was this helpful?</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              We're constantly updating our FAQ based on user feedback. If you have suggestions for additional questions or improvements, please let us know!
            </p>
